*Rolfe, Gary. [http://www.blackwell-synergy.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1440-1800.2006.00298.x "Judgements without rules: towards a postmodern ironist concept of research validity."] ''Nursing Inquiry''. 13.1 (2006): p 7-15. 

