is (author)|Sam Harris]] | [[The End of Faith]] | 7 April 2006 |- | [[Jamy Ian Swiss]] | Psychics, Science, and Magic | 24 March 2006 |- | [[Daniel Dennett]] | [[Breaking the Spell: Religion as a Natural Phenomenon|Breaking the Spell]] | 3 March 2006 |- | [[Richard Dawkins]] | The Root of All Evil? | 10 February 2006 |- | [[Eugenie Scott]] | The Dover Trial: Evolution vs. Intelligent Design | 20 January 2006 |- | [[Max Maven]] | Magic and Skepticism | 13 January 2006 |}
